    <div class="grid-3col">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-robot"></i></div><h3>AI &amp; Intelligent Automation</h3><p>Leverage AI to automate business processes, improve productivity, and enhance customer experiences through intelligent applications, AI assistants, and data-driven solutions.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div><h3>Software Development</h3><p>Secure, scalable, user-centric software — enterprise apps, web platforms, mobile, SaaS, business portals, and custom digital solutions.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div><h3>Cyber Security</h3><p>Strengthen security posture with assessments, vulnerability management, compliance consulting, risk management, and awareness initiatives.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-arrow-trend-up"></i></div><h3>Digital Transformation</h3><p>Adopt modern technologies, streamline operations, integrate digital platforms, and build future-ready business ecosystems.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i></div><h3>IT &amp; Telecom Consulting</h3><p>Domain expertise in telecom and infrastructure — design review, technical advisory, system integration, and engineering services.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-simple"></i></div><h3>Business &amp; Technology Advisory</h3><p>Bridge business objectives with tech strategy — informed investment, operational efficiency, and technology-driven transformation.</p></div>
