        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-hammer"></i> Build</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Secure</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Support</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Grow</span>
        <span class="arrow" style="margin-left: 20px;">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Understand</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i> Assess</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-pen-ruler"></i> Design</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-hammer"></i> Build</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Secure</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Support</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Grow</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Industries -->
    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Industries We Serve</h2>
    <div class="industry-tags">
      <span>Government &amp; Public Sector</span><span>Metro Rail &amp; Transportation</span><span>Manufacturing</span><span>Healthcare</span>
      <span>Banking &amp; Financial Services</span><span>Education</span><span>Retail &amp; E-Commerce</span><span>Information Technology</span>
      <span>Infrastructure &amp; Engineering</span><span>Small &amp; Medium Enterprises</span><span>Startups</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose -->
    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Why Choose VedaNova?</h2>
    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Business-first technology consulting</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> End-to-end capabilities under one roof</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i> Secure, scalable, future-ready solutions</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i> Strong expertise in AI, Software, Cyber, Digital</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-ruler-combined"></i> Practical implementation with measurable outcomes</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i> Long-term partnership &amp; support</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-gem"></i> Quality, transparency &amp; continuous innovation</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Vision Mission Values -->
    <div class="vision-mission">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></div><h3>Our Vision</h3><p>To become a trusted global technology consulting and digital transformation partner, enabling organizations to innovate, operate securely, and achieve sustainable growth through intelligent technology solutions.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div><h3>Our Mission</h3><p>To deliver innovative, practical, and secure technology solutions that solve real business challenges while creating long-term value for our clients, partners, and communities.</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: #2563c0;"></i> Our Values</h2>
    <div class="values-list">
      <div class="value-item"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i><div><strong>Innovation</strong><span>Explore emerging tech</span></div></div>
      <div class="value-item"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i><div><strong>Integrity</strong><span>Trust, transparency, ethics</span></div></div>
      <div class="value-item"><i class="fas fa-medal"></i><div><strong>Excellence</strong><span>Quality &amp; professionalism</span></div></div>
      <div class="value-item"><i class="fas fa-users"></i><div><strong>Collaboration</strong><span>Extension of your team</span></div></div>
      <div class="value-item"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i><div><strong>Customer Success</strong><span>Value we create for you</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer-note">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Building the Future, Together</h2>
      <p>Technology is changing the way the world works. At VedaNova, we are committed to helping organizations embrace that change with confidence. By combining strategic thinking, engineering expertise, and customer-focused innovation, we create solutions that meet today's needs and prepare for tomorrow's opportunities.</p>
      <div class="brand">VedaNova <span>—</span> Innovating Beyond Boundaries</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
